## 🧮 Example Calculation

```
Moon Longitude = 53°

Nakshatra Index = FLOOR(53 / (360/27))
                 = FLOOR(53 / 13.333333)
                 = FLOOR(3.975)
                 = 3

Nakshatra = Rohini
```

